,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"米歇爾","body":"呃，你在意的，居然是那個嗎？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"m_surprised","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"ev186-ep5-028","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":13}],"windowDisplayName":"育美","body":"嗯－，如果是一天的話，育美可能還能忍耐……\n但一輩子都不能吃的話就有點討厭了。\n該怎麼辦才好呢……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":13,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":13,"voiceId":"ev186-ep5-029","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":15}],"windowDisplayName":"米歇爾","body":"不用緊張喔～，小育。\n這些都只是「假設」而已～","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":15,"motionName":"m_nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":15,"voiceId":"ev186-ep5-030","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":13}],"windowDisplayName":"育美","body":"而且，要是一直都是瑪麗……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":13,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":13,"voiceId":"ev186-ep5-031","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenS